      <h3 class="title"><a href="/blog/national-security-technology-and-liberty/edward-snowden-talk-privacy-tech-community-sxsw" rel="bookmark" title="Edward Snowden to Talk Privacy With the Tech Community at SXSW">Edward Snowden to Talk Privacy With the Tech Community at SXSW</a></h3>
      <div class="metadata metadata-top clearfix">
        <div class="blogDate">03/04/2014</div>
